text: Eunidia unifuscomaculata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1960.BioLib.cz - Eunidia unifuscomaculata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1960
